      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 16:39:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼将意大利高额债务归咎于改革进程中的不稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/meloni-blames-sky-high-debt-on-italy-instability-in-reform-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼将意大利巨额债务与其政府不稳定的历史联系起来，这预示着她将如何在未来的公投中为像她这样的总理争取更强有力的授权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/meloni-blames-sky-high-debt-on-italy-instability-in-reform-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 16:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰将分析是否重新开放白俄罗斯边境口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/poland-to-analyze-whether-to-reopen-one-belarus-border-crossing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克在东部城市比亚韦斯托克的一次集会上表示，波兰将研究是否重新开放与白俄罗斯的一个边境口岸，以促进当地社区之间的贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/poland-to-analyze-whether-to-reopen-one-belarus-border-crossing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 15:59:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油公司债务上限威胁后哥伦比亚债券和比索下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/colombia-bonds-peso-drop-after-petro-threats-over-debt-ceiling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗威胁称，如果立法者拒绝批准提高该国债务上限，他将“停止付款”，导致哥伦比亚债券和货币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/colombia-bonds-peso-drop-after-petro-threats-over-debt-ceiling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 15:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
